  "title": "AB03 - After-School Programme Student Mentor",
  "description": "<ul><li>Student Care Mentor</li><li>Monday - Friday 12.30pm to 8pm </li><li>Address: Tampines </li><li>Salary: $1800 - $2100 </li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Overview:</strong></u><br />As a Student Care Mentor, you will support the daily care and development of children, ensuring a safe, engaging, and structured environment in the centre.</p><p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><ol><li>Provide daily care, supervision, and guidance to children in the centre</li><li>Fetch children from schools or designated pick-up points</li><li>Support children with homework and school-related work</li><li>Conduct simple enrichment or tuition activities when required</li><li>Assist with daily routines, including tea breaks and mealtimes </li><li>Support the planning and execution of holiday programmes and activities</li><li>Communicate daily updates or observations to supervisors</li><li>Maintain general cleanliness and housekeeping standards within the centre</li><li>Follow centre policies and safety procedures at all times</li><li>Carry out any other duties as assigned by the Centre Supervisor/ Management</li></ol><p><u><strong>Requirements: </strong></u></p><ul><li>With student care teacher experiences preferred. </li></ul><p><u><strong>Remark:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Shift work is required during school holiday </li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
